---
title: Herby Lamb Rump & Roast Beetroot Salad with Baby Broccoli, Caramelised Onion & Mayo
description: It's roast lamb, but not as you know it! We're using our flavourful and earthy herb and mushroom seasoning to lift succulent lamb rump to new heights. With a generous helping of roasted veggies, it's all you need to create a nutritious meal that's fit for even the
fussiest eaters.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smokey-lamb-roasted-beetroot-salad-b1954f46.jpg
